  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "In a bowl, whisk together lime juice, lime zest, ginger, garlic, salt, and pepper.",
    "Add the king prawns to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Heat the coconut oil in a skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the marinated prawns to the skillet and cook for 2-3 minutes per side.",
    "Transfer the skillet to the preheated oven and bake for 5-7 minutes.",
    "Serve the prawns hot with additional lime wedges if desired."
